Database for Anchor Model

Load data frame from 1_data analysis.Rmd I calculated percent wetland, forest, and shrub riparian cover in GIS by buffering stream by 30m, converted nlcd raster to polygon, used select function to save individual polygon layers of wetland, forest, and shrub. Used Tabulate intersection function to get tables by rca_id or percent overlap and then joined tables to rca shapefile. The covariates are joined individually to the anchor dataframe here. Code also replaces NA with 0 for all 3 covariates.Remove month of April.
